### Test API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:3002/api

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3002/api

### 2. Get All Portfolios
GET http://localhost:3002/api/portfolios

### 3. Get Categories
GET http://localhost:3002/api/portfolios/categories

### 4. Get Single Portfolio (replace {id} with actual ID)
GET http://localhost:3002/api/portfolios/{id}

### 5. Create Portfolio
POST http://localhost:3002/api/portfolios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Project",
  "createdBy": "John Doe",
  "year": "2024",
  "category": "Web Development",
  "description": "This is a test project description",
  "images": [
    "https://example.com/image1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/image2.jpg"
  ]
}

### 6. Update Portfolio (replace {id} with actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/portfolios/{id}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Project Title",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### 7. Delete Portfolio (replace {id} with actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/portfolios/{id}
